  "text": "As was found in this study, Van Esbroeck et al. [CITATION_1] , working in Alberta, Canada, found smooth bromegrass produced lower regrowth yields than meadow and hybrid bromegrass. Seven weeks of regrowth during August and September at 52\u02daN lat. produced 2.3 Mg ha \u22121 for meadow and hybrid bromegrass compared with 1.7 Mg ha \u22121 for smooth bromegrass. Differences in precipitation during",
